  "strategy_re_buy_increase_tip_of_sell_side" : "The price difference percentage that triggers DCA orders. When price rises by the preset percentage, a DCA order will be sent to market to increase your position and therefore increase the average cost. If the price of the DCA order is higher than the liquidation price, or if the price difference from the initial order exceeds the Maximum Order Price Deviation, the DCA order will not be placed.",
